  "texts": [
    "Instead, I'm **generating a description based on patterns in the training data** --specifically, the vast amount of technical documentation, research papers, and public explanations about how AI systems like me are built and function.",
    "So, to your point: *How do I know these explanations are accurate, rather than just sounding convincing?",
    "* The answer lies in **alignment with external evidence**, not internal awareness.",
    "---### How My Self-Description Works 1.",
    "**I Was Trained on AI Research** -My training data includes thousands of papers from sources like arXiv, conference proceedings ( NeurIPS, ICML), blog posts from AI labs (OpenAI, DeepMind, Anthropic), and technical documentation."
